#

Vanilla Bean Pastry Cream Eclairs

$15
250 kcal
Difficulty: 75%
Servings: 8

Allergens:

DairyEggsGluten

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Tags:

DessertPastryFrench

Description

Light and airy choux pastry filled with a rich vanilla bean pastry cream.

Ingredients

  • Whole milk: 2 cups
  • Vanilla bean: 1
  • Egg yolks: 5
  • Granulated sugar: 1/2 cup
  • Cornstarch: 1/4 cup
  • Unsalted butter: 2 tbsp
  • Water: 1 cup
  • Unsalted butter: 8 tbsp
  • All-purpose flour: 1 cup
  • Eggs: 4
  • Salt: 1/4 tsp
  • Powdered sugar: for dusting
